<div class="rte">
    
<h1>TAKE THIS COURSE IF YOU DON'T LIKE GROUPS &amp; WANT A LOW PRESSURE, &nbsp;STEP BY STEP, &nbsp;SPECIALIZED TRAINING EXPERIENCE&nbsp;</h1>
<p>Exclusive 1 on 1 Weapons training in your preferred platform of pistol, rifle, or &nbsp;combination of both. Come train with us in AZ or we can travel to you anywhere.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Curriculum is a full day based off of students preference. &nbsp;</p>
<p>Method will provide meals, gear rental and ammunition if necessary.</p>
<p>&nbsp;Student is also welcome to bring their own gear and weapons platforms however, we have all necessary gear available should you need. &nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>

